node.text: White House Press Secretary Jen Psaki is in hot water over a tweet in which she called for transparency from the Trump administration amid the Ukraine impeachment hoax. In 2019 Psaki tweeted, "It is not just the call transcript. The whistleblower complaint would likely have more details. We need both. And not just the call.”  Will Psaki give us the transparency she demanded from Trump’s team? Lara Trump and Kayleigh McEnany will weigh in TONIGHT on “Hannity.”
